sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Dev as Developer
participant GH as GitHub Actions
participant Runner as Runner
participant Repo as Repo

Dev->>GH: triggers "Build and deploy Jekyll site to Pages" (push, workflow_dispatch)
GH->>Runner: dispatch workflow run
Runner->>Repo: checkout (if configured)

Note over Runner: job build\nruns-on: ubuntu-latest
Runner->>Runner: uses actions/checkout@v4
Runner->>Repo: git checkout

Runner->>Runner: uses ruby/setup-ruby@v1

Runner->>Runner: Build with Jekyll

Runner->>Runner: uses actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3

Runner-->>GH: job "build" complete

Note over Runner: job deploy\nruns-on: ubuntu-latest
GH-->>GH: needs build -> deploy
Runner->>Runner: uses actions/deploy-pages@v4

Runner-->>GH: job "deploy" complete

GH-->>Dev: workflow finished (success/fail)
